Text.Value: *You recall Haarlep's words: 'Every time I make love in your shape, you will know. You will know.'*
I can't imagine getting bored of all that myself, but you never know.

EditorData.NodeContext: Referring to the player's rockin' body (this line appears if Astarion is in a relationship with you)

Text.Value: Well, let us hope you cannot catch anything this way.

EditorData.NodeContext: Has just heard the avatar make a sexual moan out of the blue, in public, from the incubus' curse. Snort of suppressed amusement - player chose this, and is paying for it now.

Text.Value: Have you no dignity? Control yourself.
Try to ignore it and move on.
True, infernal creatures can be fickle. Let's hope he gets bored.
It's just a little friendly advice: don't underestimate how this curse will get to your head, in time.
I know what it's like to lose control over your own body. It's a wretched thing.
Gross.

EditorData.NodeContext: Wince in repulsion. Listening to the player moan.

Text.Value: *The sensation goes. But it could return at any point. How many hundreds of times will Haarlep use your person?*
Indeed? I wouldn't dare deny you your self-pleasures. But do clean up after yourself.
Well. If you must indulge, might I suggest some place more secluded next time?
'Care' is a strong word.
That's not the point - you shouldn't have to 'put up with it'.
It's not so bad. I can put up with it.
My. You must find the city very appealing to be making those sorts of noises out in public...
If you must indulge yourself like that, please do it quietly.
*One last tingle up your spine leads to a stifled moan, you struggle not to cry out in public.*
I heard that moan. It's the incubus, isn't it? Enjoying your body?
*A single shiver. A feeling barely perceptible, but you can sense it nonetheless. A phantom caress, hands dancing over your skin.*
Mmmmn...
Unlike you to care all of a sudden.
Shudder and shake it off.
Just as I get free from bondage, you fall into it. It'd be funny if it was anyone but you, my love.
I may as well just try to enjoy it.
My friend? Are you hurt? Show us where you are wounded, so that we might help!

Text.Value: Enjoy the feeling discreetly.
*As a blushing flush runs through you, you rejoice, anticipating all the pleasures you will feel, without the world knowing.*
I hope Haarlep gets bored of turning into me after a while.
I thought the same, once. It didn't last.
Normally such sounds would be most welcome, but perhaps not right now...
*Though you stand alone, it is almost as if the air itself is undressing you.*
I know what's done is done - you made your vow. But I'm sorry all the same.
Stifle the moan that seeks to escape you.
Gods, though I've become untouchable, my precious treasure has been violated still.

Synopsis:
While the player is walking over a banter spot in LOW, they experience a sudden shiver and a shock, physically feeling Haarlep connecting to their body to turn into it. They realise they are going to have to endure knowing that Haarlep is using their image for sex somewhere in Hell forever.

If Astarion is present, he will show some sympathy, or draw comparisons to his own experience.
